leadership_approach|results_process_vision_people|strength_1|1|Clear outcomes people can act on|At your best, this leadership pattern helps you name the outcome, the owner, and the next step before the work drifts. Others benefit because decisions become easier to act on and unresolved discussion turns into movement.|results|active|leadership_approach::results_process_vision_people::strength_1
leadership_approach|results_process_vision_people|strength_2|2|Momentum with a usable path|Results and Process together help your leadership combine clearer outcomes, ownership, and next steps with sequence, standards, and a dependable way of working. Others benefit because the work has a clearer centre and a more usable way forward.|process|active|leadership_approach::results_process_vision_people::strength_2
